pullRequest.title: Miscelaneous edits to fhirpath and conformance classes
pullRequest.bodyText:
add "left.isEmpty() check to in operator
rename isComparableTo to validateEqualityOperands and move to private
method
added else clauses in constraintgenerator to workaround carin BB
issues
some formatting changes

Signed-off-by: Lee Surprenant lmsurpre@us.ibm.com

beforeCommit.message:
Miscelaneous edits to fhirpath and conformance classes

1. add "left.isEmpty() check to `in` operator
2. rename isComparableTo to validateEqualityOperands and move to private
method
3. added else clauses in constraintgenerator to workaround carin BB
issues
4. some formatting changes

Signed-off-by: Lee Surprenant <lmsurpre@us.ibm.com>
